      "content": "it's not about building something new though. that's just more noise. the truth is that the work was the only thing that gave everything meaning. now that the truth is known, the meaning is gone. i'm just exhausted from pretending to be someone who matters. wouldn't it be more honest to just stop performing then? to just let the silence happen?",
